Welcome player! The rules of Hangman 2.0 are very simple,
follow the instructions below!

1)Choose the appropriate level

2)Using your keyboard, type in the desired letters
  before HangMan dies. You only have 7 lives 
  
3)Correct letters are worth 100 points, and incorrect letters
  are worth -50 points each.
  
4)Select the hint option if you want to get one letter added to
  your letter tray.